Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.76,0:00:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當月光照射黑夜之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.53,0:00:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳說 促使宇宙舞動著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.54,0:00:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在禁忌的決鬥展開時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.37,0:00:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神正自遙遠的地方 呼喊著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.29,0:00:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(超重神)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.66,0:00:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪惡為此而戴上了面具\N希望能以此錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.63,0:00:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換取持續戮力不停\N所追求的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.80,0:00:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為命運而不知所措之\N嘆息的玫瑰念珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.34,0:00:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因無法抹去的記憶\N而為愛顫抖著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.29,0:01:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當月光照亮黑夜之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.02,0:01:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳說促使得宇宙舞動著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.19,0:01:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虛幻的墜天使們啊\N美麗的飛翔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.13,0:01:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在禁忌的決鬥展開時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.84,0:01:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神正自遙遠的地方呼喊著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.09,0:01:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第十一話失去的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.74,0:01:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.81,0:01:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出現在灣岸\N第三地區的外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.88,0:01:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被EFA，地球聯合政府軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.55,0:02:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所擁有的對外星異種戰鬥武器\N超重神所排除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.22,0:02:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司你醒了嗎\N(雖因為這場戰鬥之故)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.89,0:02:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,造成灣岸第三地區\N呈現幾乎癱瘓狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.82,0:02:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但由於同地區的防空壕\N相當充足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.24,0:02:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了快起床囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.98,0:02:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衣服我自己會換啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.82,0:02:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要說夢話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.55,0:02:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.85,0:02:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.49,0:02:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是小弓啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.39,0:02:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫妳\N不要隨便進我房間的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.07,0:02:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是隔壁的吉美照顧你的\N要好好感謝人家喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.41,0:03:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的多管閒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.88,0:03:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳...不會是愛上我了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.25,0:03:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說傻話了吧! 快點去洗臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.23,0:03:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!這陣子你去了哪裡\N幹了些什麼事情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.63,0:03:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.67,0:03:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開超重神作戰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.13,0:03:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是、是其實呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.91,0:03:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小弓妳啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.64,0:03:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.51,0:03:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳覺得為了保護地球就算犧牲\N某個人也是沒辦法的事情嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.18,0:03:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?我聽不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.89,0:03:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.03,0:04:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,效果是不是太過頭了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.71,0:04:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙\N從小就只有接受戰鬥的訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.58,0:04:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從來也沒有出城過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.78,0:04:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是身為\N超重皇的駕駛員所必須的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.85,0:04:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是也因此造成了\N他人格上的偏差...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.92,0:04:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為跟英司的接觸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.96,0:04:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然斗牙應該因此學了點什麼\N但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.03,0:04:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯有人心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.87,0:04:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法永遠盡如人意的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.64,0:04:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.95,0:04:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起外星異種\N你這渾蛋還更像個怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像還是那麼消沉耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.90,0:05:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從昨天開始\N就什麼都沒吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.30,0:05:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙那樣的反應\N我還是第一次看到...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.51,0:05:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.94,0:05:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爺竟然\N敢打斗牙少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.35,0:05:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是雷文特訓下的成果吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.72,0:05:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪希露進去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.29,0:05:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪希露妳已經可以起床了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.04,0:05:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.64,0:05:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有受傷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.54,0:05:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.74,0:05:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎太好了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.12,0:06:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子\N他應該會稍微有點精神吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.59,0:06:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的問題\N就是那個離家出走的少年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.27,0:06:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.44,0:06:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於出現啦?你這個小渾帳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.38,0:06:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!那個男生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.44,0:06:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙弟弟他好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.35,0:06:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰管他啊那個渾球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.31,0:06:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?吵架啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.85,0:06:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是吵架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.49,0:06:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦都回座位去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.39,0:06:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦?紅小弟 出現啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.50,0:06:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦我還是擔心出席率嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.10,0:06:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.04,0:06:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可要好好的照顧你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.74,0:06:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1，2 1，2...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.08,0:07:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露小姐真的沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.72,0:07:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞞著桑德曼先生這樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.02,0:07:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫琪我不會給妳添麻煩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.46,0:07:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然會有所顧忌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.33,0:07:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但至少我還是個戰鬥班長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.67,0:07:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被怒斥的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.60,0:07:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會跟您一起受罰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.97,0:07:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳庫琪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.34,0:07:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是要是被桑德曼先生責罵\N還真令人難過啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.28,0:07:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.52,0:07:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,累斃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.39,0:07:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪個老師\N都集中火力對你砲轟的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.96,0:07:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師們也很高興啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.06,0:07:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯因為你願意回學校啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.57,0:07:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊!是超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.57,0:07:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據EFA發表說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.07,0:08:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種似乎是從宇宙來的\N機械生命體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?生命體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.18,0:08:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那~跟我們一樣是活的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.22,0:08:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過說是生命體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.45,0:08:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻沒有感情跟思考的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.09,0:08:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是純粹的戰鬥武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.02,0:08:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過還不清楚是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.66,0:08:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了什麼目的\N把它們送來地球的就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.53,0:08:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將來還會有\N更多的被害者出現吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,班上也有受害者哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是住家被破壞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.47,0:08:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或家人受到傷害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.57,0:08:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁班還有\N受到重傷而住院的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.57,0:08:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.04,0:08:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家都很高興你平安無事哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.94,0:08:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.62,0:08:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.86,0:08:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你駕駛超重神作戰的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.49,0:08:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有再重逢的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.46,0:08:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.85,0:09:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.12,0:09:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在莉露去接英司回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.56,0:09:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一定會帶他回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.43,0:09:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然身為一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.00,0:09:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但真的是缺乏了某些東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.44,0:09:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要一面臨戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.98,0:09:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的腦子裡\N就只想著要打倒敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.08,0:09:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他的事情\N全會被我拋諸腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.42,0:09:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.52,0:09:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.65,0:09:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不是英司阻止我的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.75,0:09:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會讓雪希露犧牲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.70,0:10:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好你們覺得會說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.63,0:10:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分手的糾纏、\N還是算三角戀愛的舊帳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.67,0:10:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是單戀的告白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.84,0:10:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦!下吧下吧\N下錯的就回去怪你老爸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.24,0:10:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分手的糾纏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.84,0:10:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對聯誼後所產生的相互吸引
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.08,0:10:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們太不像話了啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.49,0:10:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,私自外出嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.72,0:10:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也學會這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.42,0:10:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我擔心你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.86,0:10:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會回去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.04,0:10:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來自觀測衛星的影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.31,0:10:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩隻都是毀滅者級的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.41,0:10:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離到達地球時間\N約10分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.85,0:10:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩隻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.02,0:11:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露她?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.56,0:11:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起\N要是我有阻止她的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.36,0:11:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.96,0:11:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓G戰影\N也使用幽靈系統出擊好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.57,0:11:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.07,0:11:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子也改變不少了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.04,0:11:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位就算英司少爺他們不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.01,0:11:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也要連他們的份一起加油哦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.78,0:11:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.82,0:11:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的幽靈系統\N你可要爭氣哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.36,0:11:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都要靠你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.10,0:11:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊機領隊呼叫各機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.27,0:11:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有武器系統鎖定目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.04,0:11:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.84,0:11:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!全彈命中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.68,0:11:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別大意牠來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.28,0:12:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機群散開緊急迴避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.96,0:12:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各機最大速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.16,0:12:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別讓牠們跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.53,0:12:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.86,0:12:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙他從小就在城中長大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.47,0:12:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去了家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.14,0:12:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.64,0:12:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.97,0:12:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以稍微有點偏差\N也是沒辦法的是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.21,0:12:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我跟那種腦袋空空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.68,0:12:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是一就是二的天才渾蛋\N混在一起那可不必了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.25,0:12:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我可以理解斗牙的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.39,0:12:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我也完全沒有\N家人跟朋友的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.43,0:12:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟斗牙一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.67,0:12:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是腦袋空空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.04,0:12:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作戰不僅僅是求勝就可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.74,0:13:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼不足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.41,0:13:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信英司一定擁有那種事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.08,0:13:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.02,0:13:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.39,0:13:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.86,0:13:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.56,0:13:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實你是很溫柔的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.70,0:13:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天\N你一定會找到那種事物的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.10,0:13:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.54,0:13:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.71,0:13:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.92,0:13:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G呼叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.46,0:13:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.33,0:13:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟琉菜一樣都太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.33,0:13:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來\N搞不好真的會死人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.07,0:13:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.77,0:14:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定可以阻止斗牙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.14,0:14:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像昨天那時候一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.44,0:14:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有你在...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.61,0:14:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別逗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.21,0:14:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是他的保姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.62,0:14:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只有你能夠辦得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.32,0:14:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快看!天空...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.62,0:14:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.03,0:14:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是EFA\N(Earthfightingagent)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.20,0:14:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前外星異種自上空接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.27,0:14:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請各位市民立刻進入\N最近的防空壕避難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.54,0:14:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!快逃啊!英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.94,0:14:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!妳也快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.31,0:14:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露小姐、英司少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.21,0:14:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了!跟丟了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.32,0:14:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是失策!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.95,0:14:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟城裡聯絡不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.59,0:14:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之先進防空壕裡去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.42,0:14:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.53,0:14:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是還有幽靈系統嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.20,0:15:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想死...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.24,0:15:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防空壕還沒到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.97,0:15:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.91,0:15:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺再撐一下...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.14,0:15:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.97,0:15:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是只能挨打了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.42,0:15:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新型機到達了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.58,0:15:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.10,0:16:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.31,0:16:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們怎麼那麼沒用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.04,0:16:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我也有超重神的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.19,0:16:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.73,0:16:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊跟防禦是分開負責的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.23,0:16:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.57,0:16:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神會收拾掉牠的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.31,0:17:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙攻擊機跟戰影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.78,0:17:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是使用幽靈系統動作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.89,0:17:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得盡快解決牠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.92,0:17:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.16,0:17:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出現了 是超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.89,0:17:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.63,0:17:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是幽靈系統吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.64,0:17:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重破壞砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.94,0:17:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.84,0:17:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.24,0:17:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重破壞砲!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.55,0:17:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集中一點齊發!\N超重來福槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.89,0:17:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被定點防禦擋住了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.96,0:17:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重飛彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.26,0:17:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自動控制模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.60,0:17:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有用!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.47,0:18:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家明明調整的很完美的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.99,0:18:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子安定指數下降到77%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.53,0:18:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離重力子臨界點還剩8043點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.17,0:18:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.64,0:18:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左側重鑽機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.74,0:18:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重龍捲壓力拳發射預備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.14,0:18:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.71,0:18:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重龍捲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.82,0:18:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壓力拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.17,0:19:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.40,0:19:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍捲壓力拳也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.17,0:19:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重新月鏢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.24,0:19:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自動控制模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.08,0:19:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重新月鏢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.52,0:19:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.94,0:19:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.07,0:19:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迴力鏢技沒有效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.31,0:19:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光靠幽靈系統...還是贏不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.91,0:19:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.21,0:19:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.81,0:19:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.30,0:20:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.34,0:20:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是不去的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.24,0:20:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.37,0:20:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣\N妳一個人跑出去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.15,0:20:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.80,0:20:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.10,0:20:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小弓...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.57,0:20:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小弓!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.67,0:21:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小弓!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.82,0:21:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看著在烈陽熱氣下\N道路的那一方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.36,0:21:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,形形色色的事物\N呈現形形色色的擺動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.44,0:21:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知該為何這般\N心頭思緒紛亂不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.05,0:22:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但就這麼視而不見\N朝向明日飛去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.59,0:22:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為無法接受如此的不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.89,0:22:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才說出了這麼不客氣的話語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.36,0:22:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若只是孤單一人地強出頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.23,0:22:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換來的只有誤解\N矛盾與迷惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.04,0:22:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於那牽繫著悲傷的羈絆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.34,0:22:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓微笑的雙眸中滲出了淚水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.78,0:22:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多想將這暖意傳送出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.62,0:22:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便緊握著手一直不願放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.39,0:22:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好讓這祈禱得以傳達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.93,0:22:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊....\N人家最重要的超重神要壞掉了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.07,0:22:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點回來嘛!英司少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.20,0:22:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪我嗎?是我不對喔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.21,0:22:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回播出\N"因為有你"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.71,0:23:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來\N也會照料各位的和平哦!